styleCard.description: A relentless, rhythm-driven track with atmospheric synthesizers and a propulsive motorik beat, perfectly capturing the experience of traversing German autobahns on a long journey from Bonn to Frankfurt.

directions: Start at Winzerstraße 79, 53129, Bonn, Dottendorf, Nordrhein-Westfalen
Go northeast on Winzerstraße toward Damaschkestraße
Make a sharp left on Damaschkestraße
Take the exit on the right to merge onto A59 toward Köln / Bonn-Nordost
Take exit 39 on the right to merge onto A560 toward Frankfurt a.M. / Sankt Augustin / Siegburg
Take exit 5 on the right to A3 toward Köln / Frankfurt a.M.
Keep right at the fork to merge onto A3 toward Frankfurt a.M.
Keep right at exit 47 toward Frankfurt / Hannover / A66 / Mainz / Wiesbaden
Finish at Frankfurt am Main, Hessen, on the right
